# INSTALL

## Dependencies using distribution packages

Packages names may differ from those given behind depending on the version of your distribution.

### Linux/Debian

#### Compilation dependencies

~~~sh
sudo apt install cmake libusb-1.0-0-dev
~~~

#### Runtime dependencies

~~~sh
sudo apt install libusb-1.0-0
~~~

### FreeBSD

#### Compilation dependencies

~~~sh
sudo pkg install
~~~

#### Runtime dependencies

~~~sh
~~~

### NetBSD

#### Compilation dependencies

~~~sh
sudo pkgin install cmake libusb1
~~~

#### Runtime dependencies

~~~sh
~~~
